{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then at one stage, we have been-- we have been having some guards with dogs behind us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And who couldn't continue walking and stopped, or even to relieve ourselves-- we had been very careful in how to relieve ourselves, because if you stopped out of the line, you got shot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or you were behind, and you might have frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have seen many dead bodies along the route.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know where we are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now we, the prisoners, some of them took the chance to take clothes off those corpses which were lying along the road, to make themselves more warm because it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were-- Annetta and I were always together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were two-- we had two other friends together, two younger girls, with whom we kept together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one time, we had to-- we could stop at some farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a haystack, and we could sit around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And somebody made a little fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know if it was the guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The guard was probably in the-- in the farm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think we have been made-- given something to eat, but I don't remember details.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember only one dreadful thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those beautiful shoes I talked about before, which were so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My sister, unfortunately, didn't have those shoes-- the same kind-- but she had shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I took them off, and they froze.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were smaller, and I couldn't put them on in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I had to go without the shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had them with me, but I had to-- Annetta and friends helped me to put the straw with some rags, binding around-- binding around my feet that I could walk.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And eventually, the shoes defrosted, and I could put them on again.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
